Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know that I've ever\N{\fs36}我不知道我曾经
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,been able to do anything.\N{\fs36}可以做什么事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I say it as a sort of,\N{\fs36}我这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,because I'm aware that it can be a strength\N{\fs36}是因为我知道这可能是一种优点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,but it can also be a weakness\N{\fs36}也可能是一种缺点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,because the focus is obsessive\N{\fs36}因为成为众人的焦点令人着迷
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and so when I go for something,\N{\fs36}所以当我要做某事的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I go for it at the expense of everything else.\N{\fs36}我会对每件事都倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And I love what I do, simply,\N{\fs36}说白了 就是热爱我所从事的职业
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and I feel so lucky that\N{\fs36}我感到非常幸运
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to do it\N{\fs36}我能成为演员
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and that I get to do it for a living\N{\fs36}同时还能以演戏为生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and cinema and theater have had\N{\fs36}电影院、剧院对我一生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,such a profound effect on me in my life.\N{\fs36}都产生了深远的影响
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,It's just a gut feeling.\N{\fs36}这是一种直觉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I think I always trust my gut,\N{\fs36}我一直相信我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that's all I have,\N{\fs36}一向如此
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,even when I'm working.\N{\fs36}甚至是在我工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And you're thinking about the shape of a scene\N{\fs36}当你在想场景的布局
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and how it should be played\N{\fs36}还有场景该如何进行的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and your head can often get in the way\N{\fs36}你的大脑总会干扰
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and you've got to trust your gut.\N{\fs36}你得相信你的直觉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And it's just if I'm inspired,\N{\fs36}如果我受到启发
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,if my curiosity is peaked,\N{\fs36}如果我非常好奇
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and I want to chase this possibility down,\N{\fs36}我想追寻这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that I see in front of me on my desk,\N{\fs36}我知道坐在桌子前的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and some of you may have heard me say this before.\N{\fs36}有些人可能之前已经听我说过
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And I'm embarrassed to say,\N{\fs36}我很不好意思地说
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I always speak in metaphors,\N{\fs36}我总是通过比喻来说明
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to speak in any other way\N{\fs36}因为我不知道用其他方式如何表达
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and for me, acting is kind of like playing the piano\N{\fs36}对我来说 表演有点像弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and if the piano is the human condition\N{\fs36}如果把钢琴比作人体的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and we all have every single note\N{\fs36}我们都有每一个音符
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,on that 88 key board within us\N{\fs36}存在于我们体内的88个琴键
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and for me, every role, \N{\fs36}对我来说 每个角色
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to play every note\N{\fs36}我都希望能演好它
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and sometimes if a character or a story\N{\fs36}如果一个角色或故事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,seem to stretch me in some way,\N{\fs36}在某种程度上吸引我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,seems to offer up an experience that is new,\N{\fs36}给我一种全新的体验
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that is a different chord or a different tune,\N{\fs36}一种不同的和弦或曲调
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that is real and true,\N{\fs36}那种情深意切的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and human and accessible,\N{\fs36}深入人心的体验
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and no matter how joyous or loving or warm,\N{\fs36}无论多么欢乐、热爱或温暖
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,or how dark or painful,\N{\fs36}亦或多么黑暗、痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,if it seems like an interesting shape to inhabit,\N{\fs36}如果它是一个有趣的角色
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I know if I'm running towards it already.\N{\fs36}我知道我已经为它准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, couple of basic things,\N{\fs36}好的 一些基本的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,be on time,\N{\fs36}守时
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,never underestimate the\N{\fs36}千万不要低估
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,importance of punctuality,\N{\fs36}守时的重要性
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,be prepared,\N{\fs36}做好准备
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,you can never be over-prepared\N{\fs36}准备得再充分都不为过
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and be true to yourself\N{\fs36}做真实的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and if you have something\N{\fs36}如果你有事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that you want to say\N{\fs36}迫不及待
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that you've been burning to say,\N{\fs36}想说的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,don't ever let anyone tell\N{\fs36}永远不要让任何人告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:05.00,subTitle,,0,0,0,,you that you can't say it.\N{\fs36}你不能说
  